{
  "stem": "10859.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They'll kill us anyway.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So in meantime, they went into the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was in the garage, and they went into the house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then they see there was fresh bread was baking-- was baked up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The lady of the house baked up a lot of fresh bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they said-- they said, lady, we'll take the bread.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they put-- grabbed the bread and run away and let us in the-- they left us alone.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They left us alone, so that's the way it should be, I guess.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Close call.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We walked into the house afterwards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were sitting and talking with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In meantime came a friend of ours.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His name was Shmulek.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He lived in a village not too far from there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in fact is he lived later in Israel, and he died in Israel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he asked the man-- he was a nice man-- he says, can I come and visit the boys, sometimes?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm by myself, wandering around in the woods.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He says, yeah, you may.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One evening, he came in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were not so happy because the end was not good.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "At that time, all you have to do by yourself, or if you were with somebody.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If you were with company, I don't know what the end was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "While he was there, he had a gun, that guy, Shmulek-- beautiful, nice-looking gun.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the guy, the Polack, asked him, show me your gun.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he starts showing him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We start monkeying around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And accidentally, the gun shot out and hit him in the leg, and he fell down.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the whole house filled with blood.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He got run away, the guy, Shmulek, and left us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His wife start crying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She says, what are you going to do?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
